It is jointly celebrated by Minami-Sugata, Kita-Sugata, Hachijō, Chōan-ji, Miyadō, Nukatabe, Nishimura, and other areas. During the {{ill|lt=procession|Q11561919|WD=Q11561919|1=procession}} of the hosting household, it is customary for the Sugata clan of Minami-Sugata to proceed first<ref name=":01" />.

